<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. إِلهُ كَذَا قُلََّ عِشْ حَمِيدًا تُسَدَّدِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَلا بَأْسَ فِي الْخَاتَامِ مِنْ فِضَّةٍ وَمِنْ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>عَقِيقٍ وَبَلُورٍ وَشِبْهِ الْمُعَدَّدِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَيُكْرَهُ مِنْ صُفْرٍ رَصَاصِ حَدِيدِهِمْ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَيَحْرُمُ لِلذُّكْرَانِ خَاتِمُ عَسْجَدِ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَيَحْسُنُ فِي الْيُسْرَى كَأَحْمَدٌ وَصَحْبِهِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَيُكْرَهُ فِي الْوُسْطَى وَسَبَابَةِ الْيَدِ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وَمَنْ لَمْ يَضَعْهُ فِي الدُّخُولِ إِلَى الْخَلا<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>فَعَنْ كُتب قُرْآنٍ وَذِكْرٍ بِهِ أَصْدُدِ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>وَيَحْسُنْ فِي الْيُمْنَى ابْتِدَاءُ انْتِعَالِهِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَفِي الْخَلْعِ عَكْسٌ وَاكْرَهِ الْعَكْسَ تَرْشُدِ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>وَيُكْرَهُ مَشْيَ الْمَرْءِ فِي فَرْدِ نَعْلِهِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>اخْتِيَارًا أَصِخْ حَتَّى لإِصْلاحِ مُفْسِدِ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>وَلا بَأْسَ فِي نَعْلٍ يُصَلِّي بِهِ بِلا<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>أَذَى وَافْتَقِدْهَا عِنْدَ أَبْوَابِ مَسْجِدِ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>وَيَحْسُنُ الاسْتِرْجَاعُ فِي قَطْعِ نَعْلِهِ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>وَتَخْصِيصُ حَافٍ بِالطَّرِيقِ الْمُمَهَّدِ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>وَقَدْ لَبِسَ السِّبْتِيَّ وَهُوَ الَّذِي خَلا<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>مِن الشَّعْرِ مَعْ أَصْحَابِهِ بِهِمْ اقْتَدِي<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>وَيُكْرَهُ سِنْدِي النِّعَالِ لِعُجْبِهِ<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>بِصَرَّارِهَا زِيَّ الْيَهُودِ فَأَبْعِدِ<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>